{"tid":864613,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"尋手機 巴絲們有愛","createTime":"2018-10-16T10:30:59.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-16T12:33:48.000Z","uid":136763,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"831819f5b106a220083809c3ec971e7a6fae92d5","tid":864613,"uid":136763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T10:30:59.000Z","msg":"啱啱有個上咗年紀 <br />\n斯斯文文嘅男人問小弟借手機<br />\n打去九巴熱線<br />\n<br />\n佢話去九巴總站站台諗住報失<br />\n點知俾班車長洗走咗<br />\n落案 做紀錄等乜都無同佢做<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n佢打上九巴 響咗30 mins都唔通<br />\n佢俾返部手機我<br />\n<br />\n我醒起全能嘅你地<br />\n<br />\n佢嘅描述<br />\n<br />\n失去手機詳情：<br />\n<br />\n九巴 265s <br />\n大埔 往 天水圍 <br />\n早上730 天瑞站落車<br />\n<br />\nsumsung s9 plus <br />\n紫色機身<br />\n白色原裝保護膠套<br />\n<br />\n小弟有叫佢再去站頭 同報警 <br />\n<br />\n如有好心人發現 請tg小弟<br />\n我借聯絡返佢留嘅手機號碼<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/mkechaaaa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fmkechaaaa&d=s6l9MFVJgpHrcry9F5uOIJ4%2BuNhYgvPKbWZYs3KJomg%3D&h=b7744698\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/mkechaaaa</a>"},{"pid":"c3a1f353a8f31dcda402037394083ff4f6960697","tid":864613,"uid":193407,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T10:32:42.000Z","msg":"Up<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b455b76e124112f1fdf85550d2cdc42559627d7","tid":864613,"uid":176990,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T10:33:19.000Z","msg":"Push.  <br />\n幫推一下<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/zzz.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c5ec7106c69d7c428d3fc91b292dd362659223d","tid":864613,"uid":136763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T10:35:07.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"493bd99cf70cbce80c796d2969e6a1d4f0a036ca","tid":864613,"uid":136760,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-16T10:36:26.000Z","msg":"例牌問: 有無靈異 有無痴線佬<br />\n疑犯係連老闆?"},{"pid":"7511a2d5a877938ccc27b24443caa5e9a0805b32","tid":864613,"uid":136763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0